</section>



<!-- Open Health Stack overview -->
<section id='ohs-overview'>
  <div id='sense-summary' data-speed='5' data-type="background">
    <div class='parallax-banner'>
      <img id='sense-logo' class='pull-right' src='/images/sense-logo.png'></img>
      <div class='banner-text'>
        <span class='banner-heading'>Check your vital signs.<br/><span class="text-muted">And Earth's too.</span></span>
        <p>A tricorder for the globe, SENSE is a pocket-size device that takes environmental and health measurements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id='myoasis-summary' data-speed='5' data-type="background">
    <div class='parallax-banner'>
      <div id='myoasis-logo' class='pull-left'></div>
      <div id='myoasis-banner' class='banner-text pull-right'>
        <span class='banner-heading'>The data you need,<br> <span class='text-muted'>at your fingertips.</span></span>
        <p>Sync and upload to KEEP, then the get actionalable, at-a-glance metrics you need to improve your health and the health of your surroundings.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id='keep-summary' data-speed='5' data-type="background">
    <div class='parallax-banner'>
      <img id='keep-logo' class='pull-right' src='/images/keep-logo.png'></img>
        <span class='banner-heading'>Together we can tell our story.</span>
        <p>Secure data storage and analytics in the cloud, KEEP protects your privacy and something about data visualizations.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
